The,GILDA,Beamline,a,collaborative,Italian,research,project,is,a,general,purpose,beamline,using,a,bending,magnet,source,It,is,mainly,dedicated,to,the,investigation,of,local,structures,The,GILDA,Beamline,API,provides,methods,for,calculations,in,Synchrotron,Radiation,X,ray,science,and,structural,modelization,The,parameters,are,passed,in,REST,form,and,the,response,is,JSON,A,first,series,of,methods,deals,with,ion,chambers,permitting,to,calculate,absorpion,gas,pressure,and,read,photon,flux,A,second,series,is,devoted,to,structural,modelization,via,the,Bond,Valence,Method,This,is,a,freely,accessible,API,that,requires,no,authentication